{"tid":8281,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"請教悉尼自駕遊","createTime":"2016-11-28T09:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T09:07:44.000Z","uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1670af7f0540db04214177dca6261157e11fca21","tid":8281,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"過兩星期就會去悉尼<br />\n諗住其中一、兩日會自駕遊<br />\n去吓附近嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n想請教下<br />\n<br />\n1）係咪一定要攞國際牌，我見上網話有香港牌就得<br />\n2）有無租車公司介紹？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b17855580875d6a56b3381aad473baab9f1397","tid":8281,"uid":23763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過兩星期就會去悉尼<br />\n諗住其中一、兩日會自駕遊<br />\n去吓附近嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n想請教下<br />\n<br />\n1）係咪一定要攞國際牌，我見上網話有香港牌就得<br />\n2）有無租車公司介紹？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1) 要<br />\n<br />\n2)第一次去租大公司有多啲保障"},{"pid":"8e8a8aeed834b309fddb5b1c14046021b9244ef9","tid":8281,"uid":18179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:22:51.000Z","msg":"咁我後日就去運輸署<br />\n要兩張証件相咁多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19adb43852e77fd6d596490691574a0906c20373","tid":8281,"uid":30470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:53:16.000Z","msg":"澳洲好似唔洗國際牌, 一係你到時問下運輸署d人啦"},{"pid":"420b302896fb4abf94608de598c133aa4bd514ef","tid":8281,"uid":4207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"租車佢會copy你個國際牌，所以你要去運輸處搞"},{"pid":"4ea85953b41c2751f780d25094409ff910d6a22b","tid":8281,"uid":3628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:50:08.000Z","msg":"國際牌幾十蚊 拎定冇壞嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b733673d3525b1a6a9e1a4805c845b0e6643d4df","tid":8281,"uid":44622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:12:11.000Z","msg":"如果你楂朋友車，不需要國際牌。如果是租車的，你可以問一下當地的租車公司，最好事前找一下資料，因為有可能需要不同的條件及證明。"},{"pid":"5846f48a1ea370a64b96bbba93a8621e01578c49","tid":8281,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你楂朋友車，不需要國際牌。如果是租車的，你可以問一下當地的租車公司，最好事前找一下資料，因為有可能需要不同的條件及證明。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已決定下晝去攞國際牌"},{"pid":"ec63e5db25514807cce8ee93f375afedcab7be0a","tid":8281,"uid":44786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"利申 澳洲人 都係用緊香港牌 租過車都唔使國際牌"},{"pid":"ee594fe29073a36a455a2d0e50fa34be2f2ad02d","tid":8281,"uid":44622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你楂朋友車，不需要國際牌。如果是租車的，你可以問一下當地的租車公司，最好事前找一下資料，因為有可能需要不同的條件及證明。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已決定下晝去攞國際牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n申請國際牌除了帶近照及駕駛執照外，記得帶地址證明。"},{"pid":"909bb2836c98f4a2e0ec5c13258827f2ed5ab990","tid":8281,"uid":2346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申 澳洲人 都係用緊香港牌 租過車都唔使國際牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係澳洲citizen？<br />\n係既話一定要考返個local牌<br />\n如果你夠25或以上就可以直接轉<br />\n唔夠就要考返路試<br />\n再加如果你個香港牌唔夠3年就要掛返P牌<br />\n<br />\n如果唔考牌繼續揸用香港牌就祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人捉到就可以告你無牌駕駛加洗定八月十五<br />\n<br />\n咁你係揸香港passport 入境就可以無視哂上面所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b8c231c60c66b01676d9ddb5af3bec323ddab3","tid":8281,"uid":44786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申 澳洲人 都係用緊香港牌 租過車都唔使國際牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係澳洲citizen？<br />\n係既話一定要考返個local牌<br />\n如果你夠25或以上就可以直接轉<br />\n唔夠就要考返路試<br />\n再加如果你個香港牌唔夠3年就要掛返P牌<br />\n<br />\n如果唔考牌繼續揸用香港牌就祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人捉到就可以告你無牌駕駛加洗定八月十五<br />\n<br />\n咁你係揸香港passport 入境就可以無視哂上面所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無視"},{"pid":"2772898e07403a61b1fa38b2cef83484547dfef6","tid":8281,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"已申請<br />\n都幾快手 <br />\n係排隊耐少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}